description: Provides a list of medical transcription jobs that match the specified criteria. If no criteria are specified, all medical transcription jobs are returned. To get detailed information about a specific medical transcription job, use the operation.

nested_items.name: Status
nested_items.description: Lists all medical transcription jobs that have the status specified in your request. Jobs are ordered by creation date, with the newest job first.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: If NextToken is present in your response, it indicates that not all results are displayed. To view the next set of results, copy the string associated with the NextToken parameter in your results output, then run your request again including NextToken with the value of the copied string. Repeat as needed to view all your results.

nested_items.name: MedicalTranscriptionJobSummaries
nested_items.description: Provides a summary of information about each result.

nested_items.name: MedicalTranscriptionJobName
nested_items.description: The name of the medical transcription job. Job names are case sensitive and must be unique within an Amazon Web Services account.

nested_items.name: CreationTime
nested_items.description: The date and time the specified medical transcription job request was made.

nested_items.name: StartTime
nested_items.description: The date and time your medical transcription job began processing.

nested_items.name: CompletionTime
nested_items.description: The date and time the specified medical transcription job finished processing.

nested_items.name: LanguageCode
nested_items.description: The language code used to create your medical transcription. US English ( en-US) is the only supported language for medical transcriptions.

nested_items.name: TranscriptionJobStatus
nested_items.description: Provides the status of your medical transcription job.

nested_items.name: FailureReason
nested_items.description: If TranscriptionJobStatus is FAILED, FailureReason contains information about why the transcription job failed. See also: Common Errors.

nested_items.name: OutputLocationType
nested_items.description: Indicates where the specified medical transcription output is stored.

nested_items.name: Specialty
nested_items.description: Provides the medical specialty represented in your media.

nested_items.name: ContentIdentificationType
nested_items.description: Labels all personal health information (PHI) identified in your transcript. For more information, see Identifying personal health information (PHI) in a transcription.

nested_items.name: Type
nested_items.description: Indicates whether the input media is a dictation or a conversation, as specified in the StartMedicalTranscriptionJob request.
